quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  43,11,"Oon jippinr…óo to…ďo ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Min nguurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko noon yaltinirte…óon."
  43,12,"On tak…óo nooneeji …óin fow, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óiin, ko mba…ó…óoron,"
  43,13,"fii yo on potondir e hoore majji, refti ngannditon neema Joomi mon on, tuma potondir…óon e majji, mb'on on tuma: "Senaare woodanii eeltan…óo min …óuum On, min ngonaano taaqanaa…ďe …óum."
  43,14,"minen noon, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko min nduttotoo"."
  43,15,"∆Āe mba…óani mo ge…óal e jiyaa…ďe Makko …ďeen ! Pellet, on ne…ó…óaŇčke ko jeddu…óo …ďanngu…óo."
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen?"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wewliniraama ko o wa…óirani kon Hinaranke On misal, ye'eso makko ngon ni…ď…ďita metteendi hombo suu…ói."
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kaŇčko on ka yeddondiral, wonaa o …ďannginoowo haala?"
  43,19,"∆Āe mba…ói Malaa'ikaa…ďe taw…ďe …ďeen ko jiyaa…ďe Joom yurmeende oon, rew…ďe ! Kere …ďe seedino tageede …ďeen? Awa fii seedagol ma…ď…ďe ngol winndete, …ďe lamnditoyee."
  43,20,"∆Āe mbi'iti: "Si Joom yurmeende On haajuno, min ndewataano …ďe". ∆Āe alanaa …óuum hay e ganndal; …ďe ngonaani, si wonaa hi…ďe pena."
  43,21,"Kaa ko defftere Min ngaddani …ďe ado ndee …óoo, hara ko nden woni ko …ďe njogitii?"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, …ďe mbi'iu: "Minen Min tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen e diina, haray ko e batteeji ma…ď…ďe min peewirta"."